          Please consider creating an account on <a href="https://dev.to">dev.to</a>. It literally takes a few seconds and <b><em>we'd appreciate the support so much</em></b>. ‚ù§Ô∏è
        </p>
        <p>Plus, no fake comments when you're signed in. üôÉ</p>
        <button class="reaction-button" title="heart" style="margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: -20px;z-index:100;">
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="actions">
        <a href="/enter" id="cta-comment-register-now-link" class="register-now-cta" rel="nofollow">JOIN THE DEV COMMUNITY</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>